-- Russia may support sanctions-hit firms from pension, wealth funds
-- By Alessandra Prentice
-- Fri Sep 12, 2014 01:02PM EDT
-- None



MOSCOW, Sept 12 (Reuters) - Russia will support companies affected by Western sanctions and it may divert funds from its National Wealth Fund (NWF) or from pensions to do so, local news agencies cited Economy Minister Alexei Ulyukayev as saying on Friday.

